<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Thlacam hi kan lungchung duhnak, Chimmi he chim lo he, Kan lungchung i
 a lummi mei, A ummi cu a si.

[V2]
 Thlacam hi ngaih-chiatnak thil phorh Mit-thli tlak hi a si; Cunglei
 kan mit nih a zoh i, Pathian lawng a nai hih.

[V3]
 Thlacam hi a fawi bikmi holh, Ngakchia hmanh chim khawh mi, A sang bik
 Bawipa sin tiang zong, A phan khomi a si.

[V4]
 Nangmah in Pathian sin kan phan, Nunnak, Biatak le Lam, Thlacam lam
 kha nang nih na zulh; Bawipa, kan cawnpiak ve.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>THLACAM HI KAN LUNGCHUNG DUHNAK CH302</title>
<hymn_number>302</hymn_number>
</song>